            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Hmmm....\r\n\r\nkeeping the push/pull diagnostics separate what somewhat by design (per the comment [here](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/24128#discussion_r1239364111))\r\n\r\nSo when we get a push event from the server, they go into a separate namespace and get treated differently than the pull diagnostics for the same buffer.\r\n\r\nCalling `_refresh` will trigger another request of pull diagnostics; it doesn't simply refresh the UI.",
